      • sendMulticast

        public static void sendMulticast()
                          throws java.io.IOException
        Sends multicast packets on LAN in order to find server.

        Starts sending multicast packets at given group addres ServerConstants.GROUP_ADDRESS every second, for a given amount of time.

        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - when can't send multicast packets for some of reason.
